 mortgage originations increased loan pricing built liquidity and reduced operating expenses significantly ultimately successfully negotiated the sale of the company to td bank in one of the first nonfailed bank transactions since the onset of the credit crisis chief credit officer at regions financial corporation birmingham al4  chosen to lead the credit organization as part of the merger between regions financial and union planters corporation maintained the strong credit culture of the legacy regions organization while successfully instituting new processes centralized collections special assets signature commercial approval systems centralized small business approval to improve risk management improvements in credit costs were a significant factor in meeting and  or beating earnings estimates for six quarters in a row chief credit officer at union planters bankjune   may 4recruited to lead the transformation of credit processes and improvement in credit results at union planters upgraded talent rebuilt credit processes significantly improved risk reporting and analytics divested several high risk lines of business and ultimately significantly improved credit results evp at bbtjanuary   june long record of expanding responsibility and leading change at bbt in various roles following completion of the management development program served in various line and risk roles including manager of the management development program business services manager in graham and in cary nc regional loan administrator for triad sc and corporate banking and head of business banking h lynn hartons education wake forest university – bsba h lynn hartons interests  activities h lynn harton enjoys golf and travels extensively h lynn harton blue ridge ga us h lynn harton banking profilelinks h lynn harton chief operating officer ucbi banking blue ridge ga us h lynn harton hi i am h lynn harton seasoned southeastern banking professional h lynn harton originally from asheboro nc now makes 